snippet.textDisplay: Riley, Zoom replaces Webex, not Facetime. Like every school wasn't even at the point where they could efficiently use Webex even before this so now they are scrambling and Zoom is free. With SSO integration, they can have passwordless meetings that are secure, but that costs money so just add a password to your room. Also, virtual background videos so that I can pretend to be at my laptop not paying attention while I'm not at my laptop getting coffee.
